<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>You're invited to list on Death is a Deadline</title>
    <style>
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      body {
        font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
        background-color: #0d0d0d;
        color: #e8e2d9;
        padding: 40px 16px;
      }
      .wrapper {
        max-width: 560px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #141414;
        border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #1a1a1a;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
        padding: 32px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header .brand {
        font-size: 13px;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #c9a96e;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: normal;
        color: #f0ebe3;
        line-height: 1.3;
      }
      .body {
        padding: 36px 40px;
      }
      .body p {
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: #b0a899;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      .property-card {
        background-color: #1a1a1a;
        border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 20px 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }
      .property-card .label {
        font-size: 11px;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #6b6258;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      .property-card .name {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #f0ebe3;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }
      .property-card .location {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #7a7068;
      }
      .cta-wrapper {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 32px 0 8px;
      }
      .cta {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #c9a96e;
        color: #0d0d0d;
        font-family: Georgia, serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: bold;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 14px 36px;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
      .expiry-note {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #5a5248;
        margin-top: 12px;
      }
      .divider {
        border: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
        margin: 28px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        padding: 20px 40px 28px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer p {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #4a4540;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .footer .link-fallback {
        word-break: break-all;
        color: #6b6258;
        font-size: 11px;
        margin-top: 8px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="header">
        <p class="brand">Death is a Deadline</p>
        <h1>Your property has been listed.<br />Set up your account.</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="body">
        <p>
          An administrator has added your property to our platform. To manage
          your listing, review bookings, and receive payouts, you'll need to
          create your hotel account.
        </p>

        <div class="property-card">
          <p class="label">Your Property</p>
          <p class="name"><%= placeName %></p>
          <p class="location"><%= placeCity %>, <%= placeCountry %></p>
        </div>

        <p>
          Click the button below to set your name and password. This link is
          private â€” it was sent only to you and expires in
          <strong style="color: #c9a96e"><%= expiryMinutes %> minutes</strong>.
        </p>

        <div class="cta-wrapper">
          <a href="<%= inviteUrl %>" class="cta">Create My Account</a>
        </div>
        <p class="expiry-note">
          Link expires in <%= expiryMinutes %> minutes and can only be used
          once.
        </p>

        <hr class="divider" />

        <p>
          If you weren't expecting this email, you can safely ignore it. No
          account will be created unless you click the link above.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          Death is a Deadline &mdash; Student accommodation bidding platform
        </p>
        <p class="link-fallback">
          If the button doesn't work, copy this link:<br /><%= inviteUrl %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
